&lt;h3 id="-security-in-waha-core">🔒 Security in WAHA Core&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>WAHA Core&lt;/strong> now comes with robust, built-in security features!&lt;br>
You can protect your API with an &lt;strong>API Key&lt;/strong> - and now, for even greater security, you can store only the hash of your key using &lt;code>WAHA_API_KEY=sha512:{HASH}&lt;/code>.&lt;br>
This means your API key is never stored in plain text, reducing the risk if your environment variables are exposed.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>WAHA 2025.5 - Presence, Polls, Labels and More!</title><link>/blog/waha-2025-5/</link><pubDate>Thu, 29 May 2025 08:48:45 +0000</pubDate><guid>/blog/waha-2025-5/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="-whats-new">🆕 What&amp;rsquo;s New?&lt;/h2>
